Ko au mo e Tamai ʻoku ma taha pe.
Pea kuo ʻalu atu ʻa Sisu, pea ne ʻilo kuo ʻaho fā hono tuku ia ki he faʻitoka.
¶ Pea fakataha ʻe he kau taulaʻeiki lahi mo e kau Fālesi ʻae kau fakamaau, ʻonau pehē, “Ko e hā ʻoku tau fai? He ʻoku fai ʻe he tangata ni ʻae ngaahi mana lahi.
Pea ko ia naʻe alea ai ʻae kau Fālesi ʻiate kinautolu, ʻIkai te mou vakai ʻoku ʻikai ʻaupito te mou lavaʻi ha meʻa? “Vakai, kuo muimui ʻae kakai kotoa pē ʻiate ia.”
He naʻe lahi ʻenau manako ki he fakamālō ʻae tangata ʻi he fakamālō ʻae ʻOtua.
Pea fesiofaki ʻae kau ākonga kiate kinautolu, ʻonau fifili pe ko ʻene lea kia hai.
Pea ko e meʻa kotoa pē te mou kole ʻi hoku huafa, te u fai ia, koeʻuhi ke fakaongoongolelei ʻae Tamai ʻi he ʻAlo.
“Kuo u lea ʻaki ʻae ngaahi meʻa ni kiate kimoutolu, koeʻuhi ke u maʻu maʻuaipē ʻae fiefia ʻiate kimoutolu, pea ke kakato ai hoʻomou fiefia.
Ka ʻi he haʻu ʻae Laumālie ʻoe moʻoni, ʻe tataki ʻe ia ʻakimoutolu ki he moʻoni kotoa pē: he ko ʻene lea ʻe ʻikai meiate ia; ka ko e meʻa kotoa pē kuo ne fanongo ki ai, ia te ne lea ʻaki: pea ʻe fakahā ʻe ia kiate kimoutolu ʻae ngaahi meʻa ʻe hoko.
“ʻOku ou lotua ʻakinautolu: ʻoku ʻikai te u lotua ʻa māmani, ka ko kinautolu kuo ke foaki kiate au; he ʻoku ʻaʻau ʻakinautolu.
Pea ko e kau tau mo e houʻeiki mo e kau tangata fekau ʻoe kakai Siu naʻa nau puke ʻa Sisu, ʻo haʻi ia,
Ko ia naʻe toki tuku ʻe Pailato ʻa Sisu, ke kauʻimaea.
¶ Pea hili ia, pea ʻilo ʻe Sisu kuo fai ʻo ʻosi ʻae ngaahi meʻa kotoa pē, pea koeʻuhi ke fakamoʻoniʻi ʻae tohi, naʻe pehē ʻe ia, “ʻOku ou fieinu.”
Pea lea ʻa Sisu kiate ia, “Fefine, ko e hā ʻoku ke tangi ai? Ko hai ʻoku ke kumi?” Pea ne mahalo ko e tauhi ngoue ia, pea ne pehē ki ai, “ʻEiki, kapau kuo ke ʻave ia mei heni, tala mai kiate au pe kuo ke tuku ki fē ia, pea te u ʻave ia.”
Pea haʻu ai ʻa Sisu, ʻo toʻo ʻae mā, ʻo ʻatu kiate kinautolu, mo e ika foki.
He naʻe lau ia mo kitautolu, pea naʻe ai hono tufakanga ʻi he ngāue ni.”
Pea ʻe liliu ʻae laʻā ʻo poʻuli, pea mo e māhina ʻo toto, ʻi he teʻeki hoko ʻae ʻaho lahi pea fakamanavahē, ʻoe ʻEiki:
Pea ko e tangata ʻe taha naʻe pipiki talu hono fanauʻi, naʻe fata ange ʻi he ʻaho kotoa pē, ʻo tuku ʻi he matapā ʻoe falelotu lahi ʻaia naʻe ui ko e Fakasanisani, ke kole kiate kinautolu naʻe hū ki he falelotu lahi;
